videos.description: Maryland's Blair Watson gets the steal and runs in transition to finish off the contested layup.
videos.headline: Watson gets and-one bucket for Terps

videos.description: Azura Stevens swings the ball to Kia Nurse behind the arch for the 3-pointer, her second of the quarter.
videos.headline: Huskies' ball movement leads to Nurse 3

videos.description: Connecticut's Azura Stevens sets up Kia Nurse on a crafty pass, leading to a jumper and a Maryland timeout in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Stevens finds Nurse for open jumper

videos.description: Connecticut's Crystal Dangerfield grabs the rebound and splits through the Maryland defense for the layup.
videos.headline: Dangerfield goes coast to coast for layup

videos.description: Connecticut's Crystal Dangerfield leads Gabby Williams in transition for the layup and the chance for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Williams converts and-one layup

videos.description: After missing her first shot attempt, Connecticut's Azura Stevens grabs the offensive rebound and goes up strong with the layup.
videos.headline: Stevens cleans up missed layup for and-one

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield finds Azura Stevens behind the arc for an open 3-pointer in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Stevens extends Huskies' lead with 3

videos.description: Connecticut's Crystal Dangerfield splits through Maryland's defense and nails the contested layup.
videos.headline: Dangerfield converts tough layup

videos.description: Even with his team winning by 25 points, Geno Auriemma discusses the flaws of the offensive attack in the 97-72 win over Maryland.
videos.headline: Auriemma: Offense 'a little out of sorts' in win
